code: public Map<String, Model> readClass(Class clazz) {     String name = clazz.getName().     Map<String, Model> resolved = super.read(clazz).     if (resolved != null) {         for (Model model : resolved.values()) {             // enrich with the class name of the model             model.getVendorExtensions().put("x-className", new StringProperty(name)).         }         // read any extra using read-all         Map<String, Model> extra = super.readAll(clazz).         if (extra != null) {             for (Map.Entry<String, Model> entry : extra.entrySet()) {                 if (!resolved.containsKey(entry.getKey())) {                     resolved.put(entry.getKey(), entry.getValue()).                 }             }         }     }     return resolved. }
